WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:04.280 --> 00:00:07.880
Hello, here's the recipe of chocolate madeleines

00:00:08.879 --> 00:00:16.900
the ingredients : 100g flour, 5 tablespoons of cocoa powder without sugar, 120g sugar, 3 eggs, 100g butter, 1 teaspoon baking powder, pinch of salt, icing sugar

00:00:17.279 --> 00:00:20.720
Preheat oven to 220°C (425F)

00:00:23.700 --> 00:00:25.230
put the sugar in a bowl

00:00:25.230 --> 00:00:30.649
add eggs one by one and whisk

00:00:35.270 --> 00:00:40.200
Sift the flour into which you integrated yeast

00:00:41.860 --> 00:00:46.890
add cocoa powder

00:00:48.180 --> 00:00:52.320
a pinch of salt

00:00:56.480 --> 00:01:03.480
add melted butter

00:01:05.530 --> 00:01:12.530
mix well

00:01:18.750 --> 00:01:22.380
butter your madeleine pans

00:01:22.380 --> 00:01:25.780
pour the dough

00:01:44.390 --> 00:01:47.539
Bake 5 minutes at 220°C (425F)

00:01:47.539 --> 00:01:54.539
followed by seven minutes at 180°C (350F)

00:01:55.650 --> 00:01:58.920
once cooked, unmold your madeleines

00:01:58.920 --> 00:02:01.420
and put them on a rack to cool

00:02:01.420 --> 00:02:04.920
you can put icing sugar if you want

00:02:04.920 --> 00:02:07.970
et voilà, bon appétit !

00:02:07.970 --> 00:02:08.520
Stay tuned for next recipe !

